    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.01803.002_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
                <p>You are entirely welcome to use the <choice><abbr>eng:</abbr><expan>engraving</expan></choice> as you 
                    desire. I am about as usual—not any worse. Feel or fancy I feel, relief already as summer 
                    wanes—one of my doctors</p>
                <p>thinks much of my head trouble the past three <choice><abbr>mos.</abbr><expan>months</expan></choice> 
                    is from the sun. I am almost always easier as day departs</p>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.01803.001_large.jpg" type="verso"/>      
        </body> 
